Going Forward
-------------

So what does this mean going forward?

I suspect that Microsoft will make noise about pushing for a board seat, bu=
t ultimately use that as negotiating leverage to push for even more extensi=
ve IP rights to OpenAI=E2=80=99s code and weights (from what I understand M=
icrosoft did have full access, but the access was limited to a small number=
